column5: ya but they have such beautiful eyes !!!
I love deer.....right beside my veggies and mashed potatoes.

You guys should look at getting the ones that live near the DVP before they become roadkill  But this fall, I've yet to have seen a deer on the road near my fishing holes..But I've seen them so far 3 times on the DVP and once right in the unfinished downtown Markham section.  BTW, nice picture!
Shotgun? Use slugs or just not a hunter?
Nice photos.... What set up you got there.....Nikon D300 with a 70-300 F 1.4....hehe
Nice photos whitespinnerbait!!! What camera set up do you have?
